import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './components/App'
import axios from 'axios'

axios.get('http://localhost:3001/notes')
.then(
  response => {
  const notes = response.data
  ReactDOM.render(
    <App notes={notes} />,
    document.getElementById('root')
  )
})
